Barclays of Kenya Says Base Lending Rate Is Revised to 14.75%

-- B y   S a r a h   M c G r e g o r
-- 
2011-08-31T06:00:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/barclays-of-kenya-says-base-lending-rate-is-revised-to-14-75-.html
Barclays Bank of Kenya Ltd. (BCBL) , the
country’s second-biggest lender by market value, adjusted its
base lending rate to 14.75 percent, according to a statement
published in the Standard newspaper today.  It didn’t say what the rate was previously. The change
takes effect tomorrow, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah McGregor in Nairobi at 
 smcgregor5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  